<SYNC Start=231215><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=235677><P Class=KRCC>
아버지세요
<SYNC Start=236965><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=238888><P Class=KRCC>
