<SYNC Start=408785><P Class=KRCC>
오늘은 손님이 많네
<SYNC Start=411151><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=411994><P Class=KRCC>
예
<SYNC Start=414981><P Class=KRCC>
비서가 찾아왔지?
<SYNC Start=417705><P Class=KRCC>
